This falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP), which is typically classified under cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques and architectures for sentence embedders, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of sentence embedders for tasks such as image captioning, which could fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper proposes a new method for evaluating sentence embedders, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
